data.text: Want an impromptu picnic with family and friends? Utilize the parks first come, first use picnic areas located outside the fenced area at the entrance of the park, and along the fence line located by the lower parking area. There are picnic tables and grills provided, but we suggest bringing at pop up tent for shade.
